## Code

Inline code uses backticks: `const greeting = "Hello!"`

Code blocks use triple backticks with syntax highlighting:

```javascript
function welcome() {
  console.log("Welcome to RenderMark!");
  return true;
}
```

```python
def greet(name):
    print(f"Hello, {name}!")

greet("World")
```

