## Tables

| Feature | Syntax | Example |
|---------|--------|---------|
| Bold | `**text**` | **bold** |
| Italic | `*text*` | *italic* |
| Code | backticks | `code` |
| Link | `[text](url)` | [link](/) |

Tables can be aligned:

| Left | Center | Right |
|:-----|:------:|------:|
| L1   | C1     | R1    |
| L2   | C2     | R2    |

